OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump had high
OL,7,Fhopes for the renovation of a
OL,8,Freflecting pool on Washington's
OL,9,FNational Mall - so much so that the
OL,10,Fbill came to more than $14 million
OL,11,F(#10.6m).
OL,13,FBut since its completion earlier this
OL,14,Fmonth, the Lincoln Memorial Reflecting
OL,15,FPool hasn't quite had the shimmer the
OL,16,Fadministration was hoping for - thanks
OL,17,Fto huge quantities of algae.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
