OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe 300,000-square-foot pool - around
OL,12,Fthe size of 12 Olympic-sized swimming
OL,13,Fpools - was filled with 6.5 million
OL,14,Fgallons of clean water, all of which
OL,15,Fhas since turned green.
OL,17,FCrews have been deployed to tackle the
OL,18,Fproblem, vacuuming up clumps of the
OL,19,Fgreenery and adding gallons of
OL,20,Fhydrogen peroxide to the pool, but
OL,21,Fwith very little visible impact.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
