OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,FA dead duckling has also been found in
OL,7,Fthe pool, which animals have
OL,8,Fhistorically struggled to get out of.
OL,10,FTrump set out to vamp up the pool,
OL,11,Fwhich was built in 1922, in April,
OL,12,Fannouncing that the bottom of the pool
OL,13,Fwas being resurfaced in an "American
OL,14,Fflag blue".
OL,16,FHe told reporters, "You're going to
OL,17,Fend up with a beautiful, beautiful
OL,18,Freflecting pool, the way it's supposed
OL,19,Fto be", as he held up pictures of the
OL,20,Fconstruction process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
