OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782245910
OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,F"Much better than it ever was,
OL,7,Factually," he added.
OL,9,FThe cost was originally estimated at
OL,10,Faround $1.8 million (#1.4m), but the
OL,11,Fcost has skyrocketed to $14.2 million
OL,12,F(#10.7m).
OL,14,FThe blue resurfacing material added to
OL,15,Fenhance the pool's colouring has also
OL,16,Falready started to peel off, which
OL,17,FTrump attributed to vandalism,
OL,18,Falthough there was no evidence that
OL,19,Fthe pool had sustained any external
OL,20,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
