PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782245910
OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,FA worker who spoke to CNN, ITV News'
OL,7,FUS partner, said on Tuesday that it
OL,8,Fwould take "an entire lifetime" to
OL,9,Fclean the pool.
OL,11,FThe pool has had an algae issue for
OL,12,Fyears and was drained and cleaned in
OL,13,F2012, when most of its surface was
OL,14,Fcovered with algae.
OL,16,FThe Obama administration spent $34
OL,17,Fmillion (#25.7m) on restoring the
OL,18,Fpool, only for it to collect algae and
OL,19,Fbird droppings shortly afterwards.
