OL,3,C'An entire lifetime to clean': Trump's
OL,4,C$14m reflection pool riddled with algae
OL,6,FRedoing the Reflecting Pool is just
OL,7,Fone of many rebuilds the US president
OL,8,Fplanned for the capital, among the
OL,9,Fdemolition of the White House East
OL,10,FWing and its beloved ballroom and the
OL,11,Fextravagant goldening of the Oval
OL,12,FOffice.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
